     "message": "The code successfully meets the instructions. It calculates the number of home matches and home wins by grouping by the `home_team` (comparing the home score to the away score using the original DataFrame index), and similarly calculates the away matches and away wins by grouping by the `away_team`. Finally, it effectively merges these two dataframes on the team name (renamed to `country`), fills any missing values with 0, and converts the columns to integers to produce the final comprehensive dataset."
